    ─────────────────────             ─────────────────────
    500 Internal Server Error         { 
    java.lang.NullPointerException      "status": 404,
       at com.app.Service.java:45        "error": "User Not Found",
       at com.app.Controller.java:12     "message": "No user with id 99",
       ...stack trace exposed 😱         "timestamp": "2026-04-01T10:00:00"
